</div>


<div class="episode-description">
  <div class="container">
    <section class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
        <p class="lead">Jus B Chill and Hugs &amp; Kisses proudly present: Cool Room, the chill and sexy dance show, a periodic dance party and online TV show celebrating Melbourne techno.</a>

        <p>Each episode features a members only TV audience live at the Hugs &amp; Kisses studio. Our lucky audience members will get on down to titillating techno, dripping acid squelches, and the full spectrum of weird and ravey sounds.</p>

        <div class="social">
          <p>
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/coolroomtv" class="btn btn-default btn-facebook btn-lg">Facebook</a>
          </p>
        </div>

